# std/ (standard library)

## Coverage

**100% line coverage** required for all shipped `std/**/*.li`. Run `scripts/check-stdlib-coverage.sh` after changes (when `lic --coverage-instrument` is available).

Every public export needs a `li-tests/` fixture. No `sorry`. Uncovered lines need a tracked **G-*** id in `docs/verification/provability-gaps.md`.

## Seal

User code cannot shadow prelude or std exports. After adding exports, run `scripts/gen-stdlib-manifest.sh`. See `docs/superpowers/specs/2026-05-16-li-stdlib-seal.md`.

## Gates

Same as `li-ecosystem-gates.mdc`: functionality, security, performance — std is security-critical surface for httpd and crypto.
